00:30:12,024 --> 00:30:19,647
And even in Western North Medford, there are still hundreds of tree stumps without, there should be a living tree where those tree stumps are.

407
00:30:21,368 --> 00:30:29,873
And so I'm incredibly in favor of expanding our forestry budget to really dramatically beef up our tree canopy in Medford.

408
00:30:30,353 --> 00:30:32,014
And it all comes down to funding, right?

409
00:30:32,034 --> 00:30:33,095
A lot of people are like, how can we do it?

410
00:30:33,115 --> 00:30:34,276
It all comes down to funding.

411
00:30:34,356 --> 00:30:41,240
So again, that 48 million will help, but revising Mystic Avenue to increase tax revenue is going to help.

412
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:46,043
And then if the community wants to look at it, you know, a lot of people talk about a two and a half override.

413
00:30:46,543 --> 00:30:50,625
And it's a really contentious issue in this community because people feel strongly on both sides.

