00:41:28,351 --> 00:41:33,274
seven to eight, and so get out and vote, bring your friends, bring your family, it matters.

596
00:41:33,354 --> 00:41:36,215
It matters so much who we pick right now.

597
00:41:36,335 --> 00:41:38,416
So I hope people are feeling that urgency.

598
00:41:38,517 --> 00:41:46,461
I know I am, but I've also been doing this for six months and it's been awesome, but I'm also so excited to see what happens here.

599
00:41:46,481 --> 00:41:53,865
I hope that our hard work pays off and that Medford sees our vision and agrees it's the best vision for Medford.

600
00:41:54,185 --> 00:42:00,187
I know I realized that I've started thinking about politics and elections in the same way I think about big sporting events.

