00:42:36,201 --> 00:42:39,703
But we should all think of democracy just like

616
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:46,468
your personal health, right, in working out and eating healthy, you kind of have to do it every day.

617
00:42:47,349 --> 00:42:49,151
Otherwise, you're out of shape, right?

